<emphasis box="[232,482,769,793]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Phorodon persifoliae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Shinji, G. O." box="[488,643,769,793]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" pagination="787 - 800" refId="ref5990" refString="Shinji, G. O. 1922. New genera and species of Japanese Aphididae. Dobutsugaku Zasshi (Zoological Magazine) 34 (407): 787 - 800." type="journal article" year="1922">Shinji (1922)</bibRefCitation>
